    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>say, $form-&gt;addElement('text', 'field-name', $options);
Then, the element can be retrieved by $form-&gt;field-name. However, $form-&gt;field-name-&gt;getName() == fieldname.</p>

<p>The reason is that Zend_Form_Element will filter ($name) before setting it. However form still has it in Zend_Form::$_elements[].</p>

<p>The side effect of this is that when doing $form-&gt;isValid($post). This field will lost track of posted value.</p>

